AVALANCHE PACKAGE

Each AVALANCHE PACKAGE includes

  • EARLY ENTRY
  • GUARANTEED ON STAGE ACCESS FOR LAST SONG IN MARS' SET
  • WATCH MARS SHOW FROM THE SIDE OF THE STAGE*
  • M&G WITH MARS
  • INDIVIDUAL PHOTO OP WITH MARS SHOT BY A PROFESSIONAL PHOTOGRAPHER**
  • PRE-SIGNED 2025 TOUR POSTER AUTOGRAPHED BY JARED AND SHANNON
  • EXCLUSIVE VIP MERCHANDISE WITH LAMINATE (NEW FOR 2025!)
  • PRE-DOORS TOUR MERCHANDISE SHOPPING OPPORTUNITY
  • ON SITE VIP CONCIERGE

* LOCATION MAY VARY BY VENUE

** PHOTO WILL BE EMAILED WITHIN 72 HOURS OF SHOW

SEASONS PACKAGE

Each SEASONS PACKAGE includes

  • EARLY ENTRY
  • WATCH MARS SHOW FROM THE SIDE OF THE STAGE*
  • M&G WITH MARS
  • INDIVIDUAL PHOTO OP WITH MARS SHOT BY A PROFESSIONAL PHOTOGRAPHER**
  • PRE-SIGNED 2025 TOUR POSTER AUTOGRAPHED BY JARED AND SHANNON
  • EXCLUSIVE VIP MERCHANDISE WITH LAMINATE (NEW FOR 2025!)
  • PRE-DOORS TOUR MERCHANDISE SHOPPING OPPORTUNITY
  • ON SITE VIP CONCIERGE

* LOCATION MAY VARY BY VENUE

** PHOTO WILL BE EMAILED WITHIN 72 HOURS OF SHOW

GET UP KID PACKAGE

Each GET UP KID PACKAGE includes

  • EARLY ENTRY
  • M&G WITH MARS
  • INDIVIDUAL PHOTO OP WITH MARS SHOT BY A PROFESSIONAL PHOTOGRAPHER**
  • PRE-SIGNED 2025 TOUR POSTER AUTOGRAPHED BY JARED AND SHANNON
  • EXCLUSIVE VIP MERCHANDISE WITH LAMINATE (NEW FOR 2025!)
  • PRE-DOORS TOUR MERCHANDISE SHOPPING OPPORTUNITY
  • ON SITE VIP CONCIERGE

** PHOTO WILL BE EMAILED WITHIN 72 HOURS OF SHOW

Early Entry Package

Each Early Entry Package Includes

  • EARLY ENTRY*
  • PRE-SIGNED 2025 TOUR POSTER AUTOGRAPHED BY JARED AND SHANNON
  • EXCLUSIVE VIP MERCHANDISE WITH LAMINATE (NEW FOR 2025!)
  • PRE-DOORS TOUR MERCHANDISE SHOPPING OPPORTUNITY
  • ON SITE VIP CONCIERGE

* ENTRY WILL FOLLOW GET UP KID PACKAGE HOLDERS
NO ARTIST INVOLVEMENT

DRESSING ROOM PACKAGE

EMAIL info.adventures.inwonderland@gmail.com

  • Two (2) GA tickets with early entry
  • Exclusive pre-show use of a dressing room for you and one (1) guest with food and non-alcoholic beverages
  • PRIVATE ACOUSTIC SESSION WITH JARED IN YOUR DRESSING ROOM
  • MARS photo op with professional photographer in your dressing room**
  • Additional photo op on stage before the show to experience the stage up close and take home a set of drumsticks**
  • Signed setlist from that night’s show***
  • Guaranteed on stage access for last song in MARS' set
  • Watch MARS show from the side of the stage*
  • Access to the Museum of MARS VIP Experience
  • THIRD PHOTO OP WITH MARS IN FRONT OF MARS BACKDROP SHOT BY A PROFESSIONAL PHOTOGRAPHER*
  • Personalized pre-signed tour poster autographed by Jared and Shannon
  • Exclusive VIP merchandise with laminate
  • Pre-doors tour merchandise shopping opportunity
  • On site VIP concierge
  • Stamp in Echelon passport

TOUR DATES

DUE TO THE SAG-AFTRA ACTORS’ STRIKE AND SUBSEQUENT DELAYS IN JARED’S FILMING SCHEDULE, SOME OF THE EU/UK DATES HAVE BEEN RESCHEDULED. BOTH TICKETS AND VIP PACKAGES WILL BE HONORED FOR THE NEW DATES.
